fields.title: Tesla Model Y 2026: What We Know
fields.summary: The refresh of the world's best-selling car is just around the corner, featuring the new 'Juniper' design language.
fields.content:
The 2026 Tesla Model Y, codenamed Juniper, represents a significant update to the electric SUV that has taken the world by storm.

New Design

Borrowing heavily from the Model 3 Highland refresh, the new Model Y features slimmer headlights, a removed front bumper fog light housing for better aerodynamics, and a new rear light bar.

Interior

Inside, the stalks are gone, replaced by steering wheel buttons. The screen is brighter, and the rear passengers now get their own 8-inch display.

fields.title: Volkswagen Scout Revival
fields.summary: VW is bringing back the legendary Scout nameplate for a new line of rugged electric off-roaders.
fields.content: Volkswagen is reviving the Scout brand purely for electric vehicles. The new Terra pickup and Traveler SUV are set to challenge Rivian and Ford.
